data.description: Gorgeous Multi-Gen Ranch Home in Traditions! No expense spared for comfort and luxury. Upgrades include stainless steel appliances in both kitchens, beautiful cabinets throughout, quartz countertops and heated floor tiles in the kitchen and bathrooms on the main level. Imagine a large enough kitchen which allows everyone in to help prepare your inspired meals! Numerous cabinets, a pantry and counter space to accommodate all your entertaining requirements with a breakfast bar for eating and close conversations. A spacious formal dining room and cozy family room with fireplace finish the common areas. The Primary bedroom and primary suite are complimented with a large walk-in closet with organized built-ins and heated tile floors. Two secondary bedrooms, a full bath with heated floor and the laundry room complete the main level. Be prepared to be wowed when visiting the beautifully, finished basement! Space is not a problem with a large family room, dining area, kitchen, two bedrooms, 3/4 bath and half bath allowing for your family to spread out or accommodate multi-gen living! The yard is fully fenced to allow endless hours of playtime, relaxation and exercise for your family. A gas plumbed patio lets your chef skills extend to the BBQ for Summer entertaining. The spa stays for those evenings when you just need to relax and forget the day. Check out the 3 car garage with the beautiful Epoxy floor! Storage galore keeps all your garage gear in order. This East facing home allows the sun to melt the driveway in Winter! Schedule your tour of this awesome home today! Close to Buckley Airforce Base, I-70 and E-470.
